---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="作品" description="项目作品 — 算电协同报告 · AI 工具">
  <a href="/" class="back-link">← 返回首页</a>

  <h1>作品</h1>
  <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">已完成的主要项目和产出物。</p>

  <div class="project-grid">
    <article class="project-card">
      <div class="project-cover" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #2d6a9f 100%);">
        <span class="project-cover-icon">📊</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <h2>算电协同深度研究报告</h2>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">算电协同</span>
          <span class="tag">投资分析</span>
          <span class="tag">政策研究</span>
        </div>
        <p>覆盖中美现状、趋势、商业机会与投资策略的算电协同研究报告。包含 10 张原创信息图，资料来源涵盖 IEA、LBNL、国家数据局、国家发展改革委等权威机构。</p>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span>PPTX · 16:9 · 10 页</span>
          <span>2026-05</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project-card">
      <div class="project-cover" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d4f4a 0%, #0d9488 100%);">
        <span class="project-cover-icon">🎬</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <h2>汇竑资本 · 算电协同战略布局讲解视频</h2>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">算电协同</span>
          <span class="tag">视频制作</span>
          <span class="tag">脚本写作</span>
        </div>
        <p>2 分钟精炼视频，拆解算电协同的投资逻辑、中国西部成本优势、产业链利润分布及战术时间表。</p>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span>50s · 动画 · 配音</span>
          <span>2026-05</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project-card">
      <div class="project-cover" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a1a6b 0%, #7c3aed 100%);">
        <span class="project-cover-icon">🔍</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <h2>PPT 质量审查工具</h2>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">工具开发</span>
          <span class="tag">python-pptx</span>
        </div>
        <p>基于 python-pptx 的 PPT 布局质量检查工具，自动检测文本溢出、元素重叠、对齐偏差等问题。在算电协同报告生成中曾发现并修复 57 个布局问题。</p>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span>Python · CLI</span>
          <span>2026-05</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="project-card">
      <div class="project-cover" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #2563eb 100%);">
        <span class="project-cover-icon">📝</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-body">
        <h2>合同条款辅助工具</h2>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">工具开发</span>
          <span class="tag">法律科技</span>
        </div>
        <p>智能合同条款起草辅助工具，支持条款模板管理、历史条款检索、风险条款审查。</p>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span>Web App</span>
          <span>2026-04</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="disclaimer">
    * 具体文件和信息因保密原因未公开发布。如需了解详情，欢迎联系。
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }
  .project-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .project-cover {
    height: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .project-cover::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .project-cover-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .project-body {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  .project-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 650;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .project-body p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .project-body .tags {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .project-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
